column2: ALPHA TO BRAVO. LETS START OUR MISSION. OVER.

ALPHA TO PAPA BEAR. THERE ARE NO MORE RUSSIANS LEFT. ALPHA OUT.
CHARLIE TO ALPHA. GET READY FOR PICK UP. OVER.
CHARLIE TO ALPHA. GET READY FOR INSERTION. OVER.
CHARLIE TO ALPHA. GOOD LUCK WITH YOUR MISSION. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA BLACK. ROGER THAT GOOD WORK. NOW CONTINUE CLEANING REST OF THE MOUNTAIN. OVER.

Assaulting is the way to go
